OL,3,CWhat power does the London Assembly
OL,4,Chave and who are its members?
OL,6,FThe assembly publicly questions the
OL,7,FMayor of London ten times a year at
OL,8,FMayor's Question Time.
OL,10,FThe London Assembly was set up in 2000
OL,11,Fand has had a total of seven
OL,12,Felections, the latest in May 2024.
OL,14,FBelow is an interactive map showing
OL,15,Fhow the political make-up of the
OL,16,Fassembly has changed.
OL,18,FIn 2024, Reform UK won its first seat
OL,19,Fon the London Assembly.
